Student: 
The student only has one possible action on the system; to view their own details. The information displayed 
is dependant on their progression through their degree programme. The system should display grades achieved
for each level of their programme, as well as their degree as a whole if they have completed it. The student 
cannot update any information, details displayed are read only.

USE CASE:   View Status
PURPOSE:    Allow the student to view their grades for each completed level of their degree programme
REQUIRE:    The student is logged in to the system
EVENT FLOW: 1. Student logs in to system
            2. System displays student's status
            3. Student logs out of system after seeing status
SUCCESS:    The student is logged out and has seen their status


